ary store formats sears hometown sears outlet sears hardware and appliance and sears home appliance showrooms sears hometown and outlet stores is based in hoffman estates illinois sears hometown and outlet stores was founded on april   the company was spun off from sears holdings in  contents  history  operations  subsidiaries  sears hometown store  sears outlet store  sears home appliance showroom  sears appliance and hardware store  awards  references  external links historyedit sears holdings spun off sears hometown and outlet stores in  to attempt to restore profitability and raise shareholder confidence sears holdings spun off more than  hometown and  outlet stores hometown stores are small hardware and appliance stores operated by independent retailers outlet stores sell sears merchandise at discount outlet stores are approximately  square feet and equipped with items such as home appliances lawn and garden equipment apparel mattresses sporting goods and tools outlet stores sell discontinued used cosmetically blemished or reconditioned merchandise with new parts sears hometown and outlet stores partnered with the national volunteer fire council in november  to raise money for local fire departments the objective of the campaign was to provide firehouses with funds to improve resources for training equipment and financial support operationsedit as of january   sears hometown and outlet stores and its dealers and franchisees operated  stores in the united states puerto rico and bermuda sears hometown and sears outlet consisted of  sears hometown stores  hardware stores  home appliance showrooms and  outlet stores in october  subsidiariesedit sears hometown storeedit sears hometown stores are independently owned stores that sell sears merchandise in   of hometown stores were independently owned formerly sears dealer stores they are a chain of smaller stores that operate as a store where the proprietor owns or leases the real estate while sears holdings handles the marketing and owns the inventory and there are no franchising fees levied against the store proprietor these stores are usually located in smaller markets that do not support fullsized sears they are signed as sears and are usually freestanding or located in strip malls they primarily concentrate on hardware appliances and lawnandgarden supplies most of hometown stores carry sears brand products such as kenmore craftsman and diehard as well as a wide assortment of other national brands primarily independently owned and averaging  square feet hometown stores are designed to serve customers within their local communities sears outlet storeedit a sears outlet store near portland oregon in  an outlet version of sears department stores located in various retail locations across the us as well as online the stores sell appliances apparel mattresses sporting goods tools and lawn and garden equipment sears outlet provide with instore and online access to new oneofakind outofcarton discontinued obsolete used reconditioned overstocked and scratchanddented merchandise at a discounted price at twenty to sixty percent off regular retail price  each store on average is larger than  square feet in size in  sears opened a surplus store in kansas city in  the surplus stores were renamed to sears outlet in  sears outlet restructured in order to manage repairs and product distribution from a centralized location to do this they established a series of facilities known as outlet repair and distribution centers in  there were  of these centers in operation in  apparel was introduced to sears outlet stores and served as a liquidation outlet for lands end in  searsoutletcom was launched as an ecommerce platform allowing customers to purchase items online and in  nationwide delivery was offeredcitation needed in  sears hometown and outlet stores was spun off from sears holdings at the time of the separation there were  sears outlet stores in operation as of february   sears outlet stores have expanded its operations to  locations the majority of sears outlet stores are companyoperated  and  sears outlet stores are locally owned and operated by franchisees sears hometown and outlet stores initiated a program to franchise sears outlet stores in  in  home appliances made up  of sears outlets sales revenue and total revenue from sears outlet stores was  million in  sears outlet partnered with the makeawish foundation to support children with lifethreatening conditions sears home appliance showroomedit home appliance showrooms display merchandise instores the stores have an internet kiosk where customers are able to view similar products price match and order products not available in the store averaging  square feet with a primarily appliance showroom design  sears appliance and hardware storeedit sears appliance and hardware stores are hardware stores that carry the entire line of sears hardware and appliances as of april   stores were in operation hardware stores averaging nearly  square feet in size are primarily located in suburban markets and are neighborhood stores designed to conveniently serve local customers awardsedit sears hometown and outlet stores received the customer engagement award from the online publication retail touchpoints for their interactive instore campaign referencesedit  a b c joseph s pete  new owners buy sears outlet store in portage northwest indiana business retrieved    worth noting in business sears outlet store opens on white lane the bakersfield californian  retrieved    a b damon scott  sears outlet store coming to abq’s westside albuquerque business first retrieved    a b sears hometown and outlet stores inc retrieved    alexandr oleinic  edward lampert buys more shares of sears hometown and outlet stores inc shos retrieved    sears files to spin off hometown outlet stores crains chicago business  retrieved    a b c corilyn shropshire  sears to spin off hometown outlet stores tuesday chicago tribune retrieved    ka