tegories with sales primarily driven by home appliances lawn and garden equipment tools and other home improvement products the home appliance showrooms format relates to home appliances and related services in stores primarily located in strip malls and lifestyle centers of metropolitan areas the sears outlet segment designed to provide instore and online access to purchase outletvalue products across a broad assortment of merchandise categories including home appliances mattresses apparel sporting goods lawn and garden equipment tools and other household goods including furniture the company was founded on april   and is headquartered in hoffman estates il see full profile competitors name chg  market cap tractor supply co  b appliance recycling centers of america inc  m sears holdings corp  m home depot inc  b kohls corp  b competitor data provided by partner content trending tickers powered by dvax  mo  sbux  bidu  amzn  advanced search stocks columns authors topics no results found video center learn morestoryful a division of news corp which owns marketwatch is a leading social media services company headquartered in dublin ireland storyful combines world class journalism with industryleading technology to discover verify and acquire original content and provide the ontheground sources news and media organizations need to tell the stories that matter to their audience sears hometown and outlet stores  wikipedia sears hometown and outlet stores from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search sears hometown and outlet stores inc type public traded as nasdaq shos founded april    years ago  headquarters hoffman estates illinois key people will powell ceo revenue  billion subsidiaries sears appliance and hardware sears home appliance showrooms sears hometown and sears outlet website wwwshoscom sears hometown and outlet stores inc is an american retail company that sells home appliances lawn and garden equipment apparel mattresses sporting goods and 